<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="19600000t" end="29600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}左半边是猴子</font></p>
<p begin="29600000t" end="39600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}右半边是螃蟹</font></p>
<p begin="39600000t" end="49600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不是猿蟹合战</font></p>
<p begin="49600000t" end="59600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}而是猿蟹合体</font></p>
<p begin="184800000t" end="196400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}我从右边上</font></p>
<p begin="196900000t" end="208500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}阿良良木学长从左边</font></p>
<p begin="208500000t" end="218500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}啊  啊…</font></p>
<p begin="222900000t" end="242100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长  上了</font></p>
<p begin="242100000t" end="252100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊…好</font></p>
<p begin="267300000t" end="274800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}自己是左撇子</font></p>
<p begin="283200000t" end="292800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}所以有时候会把左右搞错，我记得神原这样说过</font></p>
<p begin="382000000t" end="390000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不知为何坐在秋千上</font></p>
<p begin="413300000t" end="423300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}追着自己的怪异才刚出现，怎么自己就跑去玩游乐设施了</font></p>
<p begin="433300000t" end="443400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}这何止是不寻常，简直是没常识</font></p>
<p begin="703600000t" end="711100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}浑身咯吱咯吱地响</font></p>
<p begin="725500000t" end="738400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">等一下  汝啊</font></p>
<p begin="771800000t" end="780100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">拿去用吧</font></p>
<p begin="815600000t" end="821400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">快拿去用</font></p>
<p begin="834400000t" end="853600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">妖刀心渡</font></p>
<p begin="857700000t" end="895300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">无须犹豫  那东西既是怪异又不是怪异</font></p>
<p begin="901100000t" end="924500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是还未成为怪异的不详之物</font></p>
<p begin="925700000t" end="948600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">砍了它也不会遭到天谴的</font></p>
<p begin="961200000t" end="996200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果追根溯源的话  这把太刀并不是原件</font></p>
<p begin="1000400000t" end="1045000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是某个人用自己的血肉  呕心沥血重新打造出来的</font></p>
<p begin="1051200000t" end="1092500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没有了刀  盔甲武士也就不完整</font></p>
<p begin="1098000000t" end="1123800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吾已经借了她四百年</font></p>
<p begin="1171800000t" end="1184700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">神原  快闪开</font></p>
<p begin="1331500000t" end="1344900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长  危险</font></p>
<p begin="1352000000t" end="1369500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">蛇  蛇切绳</font></p>
<p begin="1443300000t" end="1470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">咔咔  干得不错</font></p>
<p begin="1562600000t" end="1575100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">62分</font></p>
<p begin="2189800000t" end="2219800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="32">{\an8}忍与盔甲  其三</font></p>
<p begin="2233400000t" end="2259200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这家伙正好拿来练手</font></p>
<p begin="2264200000t" end="2299700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">实际上  它的性能还降低了不少</font></p>
<p begin="2301800000t" end="2358500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">之前以一只猴子的形态攻击吾的时候  这家伙还会控制下雨呢</font></p>
<p begin="2360200000t" end="2378500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那可真是个麻烦的能力</font></p>
<p begin="2493600000t" end="2502400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没事吧</font></p>
<p begin="2517000000t" end="2526200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没受伤吧</font></p>
<p begin="2562900000t" end="2582500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  没受伤</font></p>
<p begin="2600000000t" end="2631700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真暖和  还有阿良良木学长的味道</font></p>
<p begin="2634000000t" end="2661100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}我说  能不能别说这种恋爱喜剧风格的台词</font></p>
<p begin="2665000000t" end="2695900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过真的可以吗？把这件衣服给我穿</font></p>
<p begin="2698800000t" end="2743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽说是夏天  可这好歹是半夜  这副打扮还是有些凉</font></p>
<p begin="2744300000t" end="2763900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  那就稍等一下</font></p>
<p begin="2807300000t" end="2814800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">把这个穿上吧</font></p>
<p begin="2862700000t" end="2897200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是不好意思  神原  把你卷进这种事情里来</font></p>
<p begin="2901500000t" end="2939100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">更何况篮球运动员是不能打架的</font></p>
<p begin="2942400000t" end="2959900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么总说这些  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="2962000000t" end="3024200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你这一次又一次地道歉  我都怀疑你是不是真有诚意的</font></p>
<p begin="3056700000t" end="3069600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂  小忍</font></p>
<p begin="3146400000t" end="3178900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了  那么汝啊  咱们继续说</font></p>
<p begin="3179700000t" end="3216800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">继续说…刚才说到哪儿来着？</font></p>
<p begin="3219300000t" end="3246500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说的是连接  吾说汝啊</font></p>
<p begin="3248100000t" end="3291900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吾与汝之间的连接  必须要尽快恢复才行</font></p>
<p begin="3294400000t" end="3340700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不然连面对这种未成形的怪异都要进行一番苦战</font></p>
<p begin="3349100000t" end="3387800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？可是这和你躺在秋千下面有什么关系？</font></p>
<p begin="3392400000t" end="3434100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">恢复连接应该是…要去找专家帮忙才行</font></p>
<p begin="3435400000t" end="3468300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吾说汝啊  动脑不如动手</font></p>
<p begin="3472900000t" end="3508400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">汝自己到那个地方躺一下就知道了</font></p>
<p begin="3522600000t" end="3544000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如此一来汝也能看到些什么</font></p>
<p begin="3546300000t" end="3559300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了  快走吧</font></p>
<p begin="3706100000t" end="3720300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哇  太可怕了</font></p>
<p begin="3721500000t" end="3739000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比怪异还可怕  这是什么情况？</font></p>
<p begin="3749000000t" end="3789100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小忍把我送到这块土地上究竟有什么目的？</font></p>
<p begin="3792000000t" end="3810800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她究竟是想让我明白些什么？</font></p>
<p begin="3821600000t" end="3859600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然现在说这些有些晚了  小忍想说的俗语大概…</font></p>
<p begin="3868300000t" end="3889200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是「动脑不如动手」</font></p>
<p begin="3900400000t" end="3935500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是「百闻不如一见」</font></p>
<p begin="3986200000t" end="4006200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}变更→北白蛇神社</font></p>
<p begin="4074400000t" end="4134400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「等吾稍作恢复  在下就去讨回吾宝贵的妖刀心渡」</font></p>
<p begin="4139600000t" end="4161700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}「吾已经借了她四百年」</font></p>
<p begin="4164300000t" end="4191400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}「让她做好交付滞纳金的心理准备吧」</font></p>
<p begin="4204100000t" end="4230800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他是这么说的吗？那个武士</font></p>
<p begin="4232900000t" end="4271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  然后他就大笑着离开了</font></p>
<p begin="4273700000t" end="4281700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么笑的？</font></p>
<p begin="4284800000t" end="4288500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？</font></p>
<p begin="4293800000t" end="4320400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">吾是问汝  他是怎么笑的？</font></p>
<p begin="4324600000t" end="4332500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">给吾学一学</font></p>
<p begin="4335500000t" end="4372600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">让我学一学？这也太强人所难了吧</font></p>
<p begin="4511500000t" end="4523200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就像这样</font></p>
<p begin="4551900000t" end="4576100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小忍…莫非…</font></p>
<p begin="4578200000t" end="4587000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不用在意</font></p>
<p begin="4592000000t" end="4616600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那是不可能的  那家伙只是在骗你</font></p>
<p begin="4619900000t" end="4643700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">骗…骗我？可是…</font></p>
<p begin="4670400000t" end="4725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个男人在四百年前就已经死了  这可是吾亲眼所见</font></p>
<p begin="4727500000t" end="4785500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算天地反转  日夜颠倒  这也不可能有错的</font></p>
<p begin="4789700000t" end="4818400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是愚蠢至极  根本不值一提</font></p>
<p begin="4831000000t" end="4840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是小忍…</font></p>
<p begin="4842200000t" end="4899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">假设那个武士是故意装成他的样子  那一定是有什么企图</font></p>
<p begin="4925600000t" end="4964400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许是为了让吾和汝有所动摇</font></p>
<p begin="4967800000t" end="4995300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以汝不用在意  怎么想都是徒劳</font></p>
<p begin="4999000000t" end="5044900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不管他有什么目的  吾决不会把那把妖刀  那把「怪异杀手」</font></p>
<p begin="5061600000t" end="5080400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">交给任何人</font></p>
<p begin="5083700000t" end="5117100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果那家伙就是猴子它们背后的幕后黑手</font></p>
<p begin="5122100000t" end="5153800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那下次就由吾亲自砍了那家伙</font></p>
<p begin="5159600000t" end="5179190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">除了这些也就没什么好说的了</font></p>
<p begin="5297300000t" end="5332300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">呀  历历  总算和你们会合了我真是开心</font></p>
<p begin="5352500000t" end="5374600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}超绝SR</font></p>
<p begin="5390300000t" end="5403600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好的  搞定</font></p>
<p begin="5414000000t" end="5462000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">例行公事和余接联系一下  告诉她已经和历历平安会合</font></p>
<p begin="5464900000t" end="5489500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是我让她带上儿童用手机的目的</font></p>
<p begin="5501600000t" end="5552100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那只人偶  貌似居然还不符合自己风格地担心你的安危</font></p>
<p begin="5557500000t" end="5594200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然我说的是「貌似」  不过看了你的脸就应该可以确定了</font></p>
<p begin="5597100000t" end="5603400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">脸？</font></p>
<p begin="5605900000t" end="5626800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">历历很精神</font></p>
<p begin="5628200000t" end="5638600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">发送</font></p>
<p begin="5650900000t" end="5670500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好好  让你们久等了</font></p>
<p begin="5676400000t" end="5699700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你好  忍野忍小姐</font></p>
<p begin="5704300000t" end="5716000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还有神原骏河小姐</font></p>
<p begin="5772700000t" end="5810700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我叫忍野伊豆湖  是你们熟悉的那个…</font></p>
<p begin="5821900000t" end="5844100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野爻的妹妹</font></p>
<p begin="5873200000t" end="5920000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">面对如此明目张胆的谎言  我竟然无言以对</font></p>
<p begin="5919800000t" end="5929800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不对吧</font></p>
<p begin="5929800000t" end="5941000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}你不是姓卧烟的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="5990400000t" end="6000500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？</font></p>
<p begin="6004600000t" end="6049300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个夏威夷衫小鬼居然还有个妹妹  这么说来汝和他还挺像的</font></p>
<p begin="6064700000t" end="6081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小忍居然上当了</font></p>
<p begin="6102600000t" end="6130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">别人常这么说</font></p>
<p begin="6132700000t" end="6187300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  家兄似乎给你们添了不少麻烦  实在是不好意思</font></p>
<p begin="6200700000t" end="6219000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我叫神原骏河</font></p>
<p begin="6221900000t" end="6242400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">职业是阿良良木学长的…</font></p>
<p begin="6254500000t" end="6262800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">色情奴隶</font></p>
<p begin="6266100000t" end="6299500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说你这家伙  这个人资料还真是见人就说啊？</font></p>
<p begin="6300600000t" end="6331600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哈哈哈  是嘛  色情奴隶</font></p>
<p begin="6333700000t" end="6357100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">趁着年轻尽情奔放也是不错</font></p>
<p begin="6374600000t" end="6401700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么  还是赶快进入正题吧各位</font></p>
<p begin="6409600000t" end="6424200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">咱们来谈谈生意</font></p>
<p begin="6429200000t" end="6477200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">首先  先让我听一听你们一路上体验到的冒险经历</font></p>
<p begin="6480900000t" end="6517600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原原委委地把你们的故事讲给我听</font></p>
<p begin="6522200000t" end="6562700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姐姐我最喜欢听别人讲述自己的人生了</font></p>
<p begin="6572700000t" end="6598600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">已经到了这一步  也就没有必要遮遮掩掩的</font></p>
<p begin="6603600000t" end="6633200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我把今天晚上发生的事情  一五一十地讲了出来</font></p>
<p begin="6641100000t" end="6678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不愧是讲故事的老手  历历  真是有趣</font></p>
<p begin="6681100000t" end="6737000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">简直就像讲谈师一样  好男儿讲谈师  就是这么回事</font></p>
<p begin="6701800000t" end="6711400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}好男儿</font></p>
<p begin="6711400000t" end="6721800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}讲谈师</font></p>
<p begin="6770400000t" end="6784200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我先说结论</font></p>
<p begin="6788700000t" end="6841700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个盔甲武士就是四百年前  小忍的前身  传说中的吸血鬼</font></p>
<p begin="6843000000t" end="6853000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">珍稀种</font></p>
<p begin="6857100000t" end="6892600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">铁血热血冷血的吸血鬼</font></p>
<p begin="6894700000t" end="6916400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">身为怪异杀手的怪异之王</font></p>
<p begin="6916400000t" end="6974800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心吸血造就的第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="6989400000t" end="7051100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说  对于春假时被忍吸血成为第二个眷属的阿良良木历来说</font></p>
<p begin="7053600000t" end="7070300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他相当于是你的前辈</font></p>
<p begin="7074400000t" end="7121600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从初代怪异杀手的角度来讲  也应该算是小忍的前辈吧</font></p>
<p begin="7170800000t" end="7185800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">喂  吾说汝啊</font></p>
<p begin="7189600000t" end="7210800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这家伙是个纯外行啊</font></p>
<p begin="7212100000t" end="7245900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这家伙真是那个夏威夷衫小鬼的妹妹？</font></p>
<p begin="7249400000t" end="7272800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}说她两句  快去说她两句  吾说汝啊</font></p>
<p begin="7275100000t" end="7299300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">狠狠地她两句  使劲虐她一下</font></p>
<p begin="7301800000t" end="7335100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">赶紧让这个大外行纠正自己的误会</font></p>
<p begin="7359700000t" end="7374700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是  卧…</font></p>
<p begin="7374700000t" end="7386800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">叫我伊豆湖就可以了</font></p>
<p begin="7394800000t" end="7403500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">伊豆湖小姐</font></p>
<p begin="7408500000t" end="7426900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我说叫我「伊豆湖」就可以了</font></p>
<p begin="7429400000t" end="7474800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">伊豆湖小姐  可是  小忍的第一个眷属应该已经死了</font></p>
<p begin="7479000000t" end="7504000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这并不是别人  而是小忍自己亲眼所见的</font></p>
<p begin="7507400000t" end="7519900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯嗯</font></p>
<p begin="7524100000t" end="7564900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他成了吸血鬼  自己跑到太阳下面自杀</font></p>
<p begin="7571000000t" end="7591800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">全身燃烧  最终化为了灰烬</font></p>
<p begin="7595600000t" end="7602300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以</font></p>
<p begin="7608300000t" end="7647100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以  他已经不在了  不可能存在了</font></p>
<p begin="7652500000t" end="7699700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个盔甲武士  不可能是小忍的第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="7716300000t" end="7725100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为什么？</font></p>
<p begin="7728400000t" end="7748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？那个…我已经说过…</font></p>
<p begin="7748000000t" end="7773100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为什么？为什么不可能？</font></p>
<p begin="7789700000t" end="7800600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="7804300000t" end="7854400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是要说的话  吸血鬼不是因为「不会死」才被叫做不死之身的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7865200000t" end="7887300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  神原骏河小姐</font></p>
<p begin="7889000000t" end="7913200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不愧是发动了猿之手的人</font></p>
<p begin="7916100000t" end="7929900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">眼光真是卓越</font></p>
<p begin="7936600000t" end="7971600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说  在他自杀之后经历了四百年的时间</font></p>
<p begin="7971600000t" end="8003300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那只吸血鬼又成功地复活了</font></p>
<p begin="8008300000t" end="8040400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">即使化为灰烬  化为白骨也能复活</font></p>
<p begin="8042900000t" end="8062900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不愧是传说中的吸血鬼</font></p>
<p begin="8064200000t" end="8125500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心选中的第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="8147000000t" end="8156600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了列位</font></p>
<p begin="8156600000t" end="8160500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好了列位</font></p>
<p begin="8168500000t" end="8230600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">既然已经说出了结论  那么下面就按照顺序  按照年表开始讲解吧</font></p>
<p begin="8235200000t" end="8264400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然  太阳是吸血鬼的弱点</font></p>
<p begin="8269800000t" end="8286100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这一点连小学生都知道</font></p>
<p begin="8291900000t" end="8326100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">铁血热血冷血的吸血鬼</font></p>
<p begin="8330700000t" end="8382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心也不例外</font></p>
<p begin="8388300000t" end="8410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">更何况是她的眷属</font></p>
<p begin="8415600000t" end="8451900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而不夸张地说  世界闻名的怪异之王虽然不是例外却是范畴之外</font></p>
<p begin="8452100000t" end="8481700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而不夸张地说  世界闻名的怪异之王虽然不是例外却是范畴之外</font></p>
<p begin="8487100000t" end="8513400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">弱点起不到弱点的作用</font></p>
<p begin="8519200000t" end="8574300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">实际上在春假时  历历也曾在太阳光底下燃烧起来</font></p>
<p begin="8578000000t" end="8602200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而在那之后  你的身体不是也恢复了么？</font></p>
<p begin="8606800000t" end="8649800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我都知道的  同样的事情也发生在了初代的身上</font></p>
<p begin="8653500000t" end="8664800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这么回事</font></p>
<p begin="8667300000t" end="8697900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然他并不是像历历那样出于过失</font></p>
<p begin="8697900000t" end="8734700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是故意想死才将自己置身于太阳之下</font></p>
<p begin="8737400000t" end="8769900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许并不应该说是自杀末遂  而是自杀失败</font></p>
<p begin="8775900000t" end="8811000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}当然  他的复活也花了一些时间</font></p>
<p begin="8818300000t" end="8837000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是短短的四百年</font></p>
<p begin="8842900000t" end="8898800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">更加准确地说  即使从自杀失败开始经过了四百年  即使时至现代</font></p>
<p begin="8898800000t" end="8932600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">初代也没能完全复活</font></p>
<p begin="8939600000t" end="8978400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">和盔甲武士当面对峙过的历历应该清楚</font></p>
<p begin="8982200000t" end="9022200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你也能感觉到那个盔甲武士正在渐渐变强吧</font></p>
<p begin="9026400000t" end="9055200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而准确来说他并不是在变强</font></p>
<p begin="9061900000t" end="9096900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是在恢复  正在走向解放</font></p>
<p begin="9103600000t" end="9126500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正在向完全体恢复</font></p>
<p begin="9135300000t" end="9184100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他对你和神原骏河小姐进行能量吸取也是因为这个原因</font></p>
<p begin="9187400000t" end="9206200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这相当于食补</font></p>
<p begin="9210800000t" end="9240200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就像小忍因那类以怪异的东西而留下的擦伤</font></p>
<p begin="9240200000t" end="9271900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可以通过吃掉那类似怪异的东西进行恢复</font></p>
<p begin="9277900000t" end="9310900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该说你这个第二代也是令人佩服  历历</font></p>
<p begin="9313400000t" end="9356700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是你为初代的迅速恢复提供了帮助</font></p>
<p begin="9360900000t" end="9403400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不不  我并不是特指今天晚上发生的事情</font></p>
<p begin="9405900000t" end="9447700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是指你的个性  还有你出于这一点所做出的所有表现</font></p>
<p begin="9453100000t" end="9473100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你听不懂我在说什么？</font></p>
<p begin="9476000000t" end="9499800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没关系  你很快就会明白的</font></p>
<p begin="9505200000t" end="9566500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">反过来说  我本来是想在事态变成这样之前就解决此事的</font></p>
<p begin="9572800000t" end="9598200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">本来想靠余接一个人尽量解决的</font></p>
<p begin="9606600000t" end="9631600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过有好几个地方都让我算错了</font></p>
<p begin="9636600000t" end="9682100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然我什么都知道  但这并不意味着什么都能如愿</font></p>
<p begin="9687500000t" end="9700000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">特别是在历历</font></p>
<p begin="9702900000t" end="9762600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">像你这样不按规矩行事  行动无法预测的无轨道的年轻人面前</font></p>
<p begin="9767600000t" end="9825900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以我负起计算失误的责任  亲自来到了前线</font></p>
<p begin="9825900000t" end="9853500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是来寻求你的协助</font></p>
<p begin="9859700000t" end="9938600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许你觉得是我这个坏心眼的姐姐把你卷进了麻烦的工作</font></p>
<p begin="9941900000t" end="9973600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但姐姐这是在给你一个机会</font></p>
<p begin="9978200000t" end="10019900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为自己闯的祸负责的大好机会</font></p>
<p begin="10024900000t" end="10052400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过我这么说你也不可能马上就能理解</font></p>
<p begin="10057800000t" end="10085000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许一辈子都没法理解</font></p>
<p begin="10092000000t" end="10132900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但是历历  你就从来都没有想过吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10134600000t" end="10190900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为什么你这半年来  几乎每个月都会遇到麻烦的怪异现象</font></p>
<p begin="10194200000t" end="10211300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你就不觉得奇怪吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10214700000t" end="10274300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">为什么传说中的吸血鬼姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心</font></p>
<p begin="10274300000t" end="10329800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">会在春假的时候  全世界哪儿也没去  偏偏到访了你住的这个小镇</font></p>
<p begin="10335990000t" end="10349000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这只是一个偶然吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10353590000t" end="10366500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">螃蟹女孩</font></p>
<p begin="10367700000t" end="10382800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">蜗牛女孩</font></p>
<p begin="10384400000t" end="10395690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">猴子女孩</font></p>
<p begin="10397400000t" end="10422000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">还有蛇女孩都住在这个城市</font></p>
<p begin="10427800000t" end="10497000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">连我都难以应付的学妹  影缝她盯上的不死鸟怪异也住在这个小镇</font></p>
<p begin="10500000000t" end="10524100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你觉得这些都只是偶然吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10530400000t" end="10567100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只有猫的情况或许有些特殊</font></p>
<p begin="10574200000t" end="10628800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也正是如此  盔甲武士才不小心踩了老虎的尾巴</font></p>
<p begin="10630100000t" end="10668000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从这种意义上讲  「偶然」还真是对你钟爱有加啊</font></p>
<p begin="10678000000t" end="10699300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老虎  呵呵</font></p>
<p begin="10706400000t" end="10741900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对于曾经全身化为火球的初代来说</font></p>
<p begin="10744600000t" end="10776700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">{\an8}<font size="33">此处原文为「火炎和火焰」</font></font></p>
<p begin="10744800000t" end="10776900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">火灾和火焰也是一种心理阴影</font></p>
<p begin="10780700000t" end="10807800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">自然会选择暂且撤退</font></p>
<p begin="10814900000t" end="10861100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果你还能活着见到羽川翼妹妹  记得一定要好好谢谢她</font></p>
<p begin="10867800000t" end="10894900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？这句话你也听不懂？</font></p>
<p begin="10901200000t" end="10922500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那你目前也不用在意</font></p>
<p begin="10929600000t" end="10991700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我是说你这个朋友即使是在无意之间也会保护你  真是个可悲的女孩</font></p>
<p begin="10999600000t" end="11037600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">自己身上发生的事情放到任何人身上都不奇怪</font></p>
<p begin="11039200000t" end="11082200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这似乎就是历历的思维方式</font></p>
<p begin="11087600000t" end="11144800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种否定奇迹的思维方式虽然带有很大程度的谦卑之意</font></p>
<p begin="11148500000t" end="11175600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而其中却有一个巨大的瑕疵</font></p>
<p begin="11175400000t" end="11185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}瑕疵</font></p>
<p begin="11189400000t" end="11219000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对于那些把你当做特别之人的人</font></p>
<p begin="11222800000t" end="11279100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你把她们全都当成是「错误」  这便是其中巨大的瑕疵</font></p>
<p begin="11293700000t" end="11315800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">抱歉我说话如此暖昧不清</font></p>
<p begin="11319900000t" end="11401700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在你这样有朝气的年轻人面前  姐姐就忍不住想要谈谈人生</font></p>
<p begin="11420000000t" end="11488900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果换成爻哥或许就说句「真有精神  是不是遇到什么好事了」罢了</font></p>
<p begin="11493400000t" end="11538900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而遗憾的是  我可没有那个不成熟的家伙那么宽容</font></p>
<p begin="11555200000t" end="11593500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说起来  我刚才是说要按年表进行讲解是吧</font></p>
<p begin="11596500000t" end="11613200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我就来履行约定</font></p>
<p begin="11619800000t" end="11677400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">到最后  履行约定才是通向结果的最佳捷径</font></p>
<p begin="11691100000t" end="11757500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">首先在四百年前  现忍野忍  姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心</font></p>
<p begin="11759100000t" end="11814200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个从来没有创造过眷属的吸血鬼创造了她的第一个奴隶</font></p>
<p begin="11821700000t" end="11837100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">第一次吸了人血</font></p>
<p begin="11843000000t" end="11896800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">至于故事进行到这里之前的原委我们就略过不提</font></p>
<p begin="11902600000t" end="11940100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟那些事情已经在别处说过了  而且已经是过去的事情</font></p>
<p begin="11947200000t" end="11972700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不管对你来说  还是对他来说</font></p>
<p begin="11981900000t" end="12028100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个初代从解决怪异的专家变成了被解决的对象</font></p>
<p begin="12030700000t" end="12056900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他并没有承受住这样的落差</font></p>
<p begin="12065300000t" end="12100300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他无法直面自己成为怪物的现实</font></p>
<p begin="12102800000t" end="12123200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因此他自己选择了死亡</font></p>
<p begin="12130300000t" end="12152000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">将自己置身于太阳之下</font></p>
<p begin="12160400000t" end="12184600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">化为灰烬随风而逝</font></p>
<p begin="12191600000t" end="12202100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">本来应该是这样的</font></p>
<p begin="12207900000t" end="12273400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只给刃下心留下无尽的憎恨以及怪异杀手妖刀心渡的复制品</font></p>
<p begin="12280100000t" end="12295900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可喜可贺可喜可贺</font></p>
<p begin="12303400000t" end="12325900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而正如前面所说  故事并未如此完结</font></p>
<p begin="12334700000t" end="12365600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">即使他化为灰烬化为虚无都没能迎来死亡</font></p>
<p begin="12368500000t" end="12391000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然消失却没有被消灭</font></p>
<p begin="12396000000t" end="12412700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">死却没有完全死成</font></p>
<p begin="12423500000t" end="12434600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他活了下来</font></p>
<p begin="12434600000t" end="12437100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他活了下来</font></p>
<p begin="12442300000t" end="12452500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">化为无化为虚无并活了下来</font></p>
<p begin="12452500000t" end="12454600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">化为无化为虚无并活了下来</font></p>
<p begin="12454600000t" end="12468200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">化为无化为虚无并活了下来</font></p>
<p begin="12476100000t" end="12532400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">经过了四百年  经过了那些足以令人疯狂令人烦躁的岁月</font></p>
<p begin="12534900000t" end="12567900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他渐渐恢复着自己的肉体</font></p>
<p begin="12589500000t" end="12637900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">刚刚恢复就又被太阳所燃尽  刚刚形成又立刻崩溃</font></p>
<p begin="12641300000t" end="12684200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">即使这样他也毫不认输  毫不气馁地恢复着</font></p>
<p begin="12693800000t" end="12756400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就在那令人疯狂的岁月中  不断摸索地进行着这些毫无效果的恢复</font></p>
<p begin="12763500000t" end="12817300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然  化为灰烬的初代不可能有清楚的意识</font></p>
<p begin="12818900000t" end="12882300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这种恢复只是身为吸血鬼的生存本能  或者只是某种条件反射罢了</font></p>
<p begin="12901500000t" end="12931100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从这一点来看  或许不应该说是毫无效果  而是好不可怜</font></p>
<p begin="12935700000t" end="12971600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一直无法通关而又可悲地无限地重新尝试</font></p>
<p begin="12975300000t" end="13037700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正因为没能完全继承传说中吸血鬼的不死特性  结果死都死不成</font></p>
<p begin="13037700000t" end="13040600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">正因为没能完全继承传说中吸血鬼的不死特性  结果死都死不成</font></p>
<p begin="13043300000t" end="13065900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是真正意义上的不老不死</font></p>
<p begin="13071300000t" end="13115100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果余弦当时在场  就能让他立刻往生</font></p>
<p begin="13116700000t" end="13144300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而那却是四百年前的事情</font></p>
<p begin="13151400000t" end="13214300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">总而言之  他不断地重复着闭合在他一个人身上的轮回转生</font></p>
<p begin="13218500000t" end="13243900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">甚至可能永远地重复着</font></p>
<p begin="13249000000t" end="13264800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而初代怪异杀手</font></p>
<p begin="13272700000t" end="13313200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他的执念非同小可</font></p>
<p begin="13323600000t" end="13371600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不愧是传说中的吸血鬼所选的第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="13380300000t" end="13412000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他凭借着本不该有的意志  凭借着极其微小的意志</font></p>
<p begin="13415400000t" end="13437100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">以灰尘的形态乘风而来</font></p>
<p begin="13440800000t" end="13446000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他如灰坐般四散的身体</font></p>
<p begin="13446000000t" end="13446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他如灰坐般四散的身体</font></p>
<p begin="13446400000t" end="13461900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">他如灰坐般四散的身体</font></p>
<p begin="13466300000t" end="13499400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一粒一粒坚强地  凭借着毅力  又回到了这个小镇</font></p>
<p begin="13499400000t" end="13519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一粒一粒坚强地  凭借着毅力  又回到了这个小镇</font></p>
<p begin="13557200000t" end="13586800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是距现在十五年前的事情</font></p>
<p begin="13623500000t" end="13682700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="13623500000t" end="13682700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="13683100000t" end="13743600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="13683100000t" end="13743600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="13865000000t" end="13947600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">在教室窗子上呼气的水雾中写下的名字</font></p>
<p begin="13865000000t" end="13947600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}教室の窓に息を吐いて描いた名前</font></p>
<p begin="13947600000t" end="13978000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我慌忙地用袖子将它檫去</font></p>
<p begin="13947600000t" end="13978000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}もぅ慌てて袖で消した</font></p>
<p begin="13978000000t" end="14045200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那是因为走廊中传来了你的声音</font></p>
<p begin="13978000000t" end="14045200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}廊下から君の声がしたから</font></p>
<p begin="14045200000t" end="14117300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我假装毫不在意  早早地回了家</font></p>
<p begin="14045200000t" end="14117300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}心誤魔化すように早足で帰った</font></p>
<p begin="14117300000t" end="14201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">不知从什么时候起我无法和你说话</font></p>
<p begin="14117300000t" end="14201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何時からか私は君と話せなくなった</font></p>
<p begin="14201600000t" end="14260800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="14201600000t" end="14260800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="14261200000t" end="14317500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="14261200000t" end="14317500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="14317500000t" end="14373800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">无须说出任何话语就可以注意到自己的人比什么都重要</font></p>
<p begin="14317500000t" end="14373800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何も言わなくたって すぐ気付いてくれた人</font></p>
<p begin="14374200000t" end="14443500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">即时此刻注意到这一点  然而我们已经无法再面对</font></p>
<p begin="14374200000t" end="14443500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何より大切と気付いても もう目も合わない</font></p>
